\"less +42 foo\" will go to line 42 in the buffer for foo."
      (while args
	(if (string-match "\\`\\+\\([0-9]+\\)\\'" (car args))
	    (let* ((line (string-to-number (match-string 1 (pop args))))
		   (file (pop args)))
